This paper focuses on using smartwatches for healthcare and wellness monitoring, which falls under the category of Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC). The paper also discusses unsupervised learning for multi-modal signal analysis, which is a common topic in Machine Learning (cs.LG). The use of smartwatches for data collection and analysis also involves Cybernetics (cs.CY) and Signal Processing (cs.SI). Finally, the paper mentions the use of Self-Organizing Maps based on Neural Networks, which is a subfield of Neural Networks (cs.NE).
